A simple **Chat App** built with **React Native** and **Expo**. 
This app allows users to switch between different logged-in users and chat individually, storing chat history locally using AsyncStorage.


## ğŸš€ Features

- âœ… **User Selection**: Dropdown in header (top-right) to select the active user.
- âœ… **One-on-One Chat**: Send and receive messages based on the selected user.
- âœ… **Message Persistence**: Chat history stored locally using `AsyncStorage`.
- âœ… **Basic Chat UI**: Chat bubbles, timestamps, and easy-to-use interface.


